title: Top notch seller
description: Great packaging, well packed. EVERYTHING you need to change your oil. 7 quarts of oil, oil filter, set of rubber gloves, super absorbent towel(x2), oil plug O-ring. Oil was taped closed to prevent leakage. Great job on the sellers efforts. 10 star rating if possible.
date: Reviewed in the United States on July 10, 2023

title: Delco oil
description: The kit worked perfectly.  And I'll know in 5-6000 miles how well the quality is.
date: Reviewed in the United States on July 15, 2023

title: Oil
description: Nice complete kit. This oil is never available anywhere, this is the easiest way to not waste my time when I go for an oil change.

title: Good product but not as others described it!
description:
Other people posting pictures and commenting that they got disposable gloves and towels with a next due sticker as well. I didn't get any of that with my order.
I only got the oil and the filter.
Oil, filter, and labels all look good and legit.  I'll see how it goes on my second order next month. Price of oil and filter at the dealership near me is about 15-20 dollars more with taxes. Not much of a difference but through Amazon I get it at my house and I like working on my vehicles too.
date: Reviewed in the United States on April 6, 2023

title: Cost effective
description: Everything for a basic oil change. My dealer literally charges $100 more.

title: Looks legit.
